We barcoded three specimens: the Holotype, the female RMNH.INS.24219 and the male RMNH.INS.24812. BIN: BOLD:ACG9223. The female was also sequenced for other genes and used in the molecular phylogeny (
Doorenweerd et al. 2016
). Sequences may be retrieved in BOLD and Genbank under voucher/sample ID RMNH.INS.24812.
